Module scenebuilder.core
Package com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.fxom

Class TransientClassLoader

java.lang.Object
java.lang.ClassLoader
com.oracle.javafx.scenebuilder.core.fxom.TransientClassLoader
class TransientClassLoader
extends ClassLoader
This class loader delegates all its tasks to its parent class loader but overrides ClassLoader.getResource(). The getResource() invokes the parent class loader implementation and checks if the result is null or not. When null (ie no existing resource match), it returns a dummy URL in place of null. This class loader is instantiated by FXOMLoader and passed to FXMLLoader. It avoids FXMLLoader to break and interrupt loading when a classpath relative URL is unresolved.
